-interest-rates-trade-policy-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eavoid%20inflation%20flaring%20back%20up%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20both%20seem%20destined%20to%20collide%2C%20as%20the%20Fed%20will%20almost%20certainly%20hold%20rates%20steady%2C%20going%20against%20Trump's%20wishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20might%20incense%20Trump.%20He's%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-jerome-powell-feud-rivalry-interest-rates-stocks-economy-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethreatened%20to%20fire%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Powell%20and%20called%20him%20%26quot%3Ba%20total%20stiff%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20cuts.%20However%2C%20as%20JPMorgan%20analysts%20point%20out%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cuts-trump-inflation-expectations-recession-stagflation-fomc-meeting-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20Fed's%20hands%20are%20somewhat%20tied%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20writes%20Business%20Insider's%20Filip%20De%20Mott.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20key%20culprit%20is%20rising%20concerns%20about%20inflation.%20March's%20reading%20showed%20it's%20trending%20downward%2C%20which%20is%20good%20for%20rate%20cuts%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20major%20caveat%3A%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20a%20dozen%20major%20brands%20have%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-raising-prices-increases-trump-tariffs-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etariffs%20will%20increase%20consumer%20costs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20with%20the%20latest%20inflation%20report%20coming%20shortly%20after%20those%20tariffs%20were%20implemented%2C%20their%20impact%20wasn't%20necessarily%20baked%20into%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20those%20price%20hikes%20work%20through%20the%20economy%2C%20inflation%20data%20is%20bound%20to%20tick%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhile%20some%20see%20dark%20c