eschooling%20endeavor.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20quickly%20became%20involved%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fback-to-school-season-homeschooling-benefits-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomeschooling%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20participating%20in%20book%20clubs%2C%20field%20trips%2C%20and%20park%20days.%20We%20hired%20tutors%20for%20subjects%20like%20English%20and%20math%2C%20but%20my%20husband%20had%20a%20vision%20of%20creating%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3BRenaissance%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20he%20described%20as%20kids%20having%20a%20classical%20education%20grounded%20in%20literature%2C%20debate%2C%20music%2C%20and%20art.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20vision%20sounded%20delightful%2C%20there%20were%20many%20days%20when%20the%20boys%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsibling-rivalry%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esquabbled%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20each%20other%20or%20resisted%20our%20attempts%20to%20teach%20them.%20There%20were%20also%20plenty%20of%20days%20when%20they%20felt%20bored%20and%20isolated%2C%20and%20I%20found%20myself%20regretting%20our%20choice%2C%20missing%20the%20quiet%2C%20freedom%2C%20and%20joy%20of%20an%20empty%20house%20five%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22908de682-b386-4236-9bbd-d819ede5842b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20kids%20thrived%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20everything%20worked%20out.%20Our%20older%20son%2C%20who%20displayed%20an%20early%20aptitude%20for%20classical%20piano%2C%20was%20able%20to%20devote%20himself%20entirely%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-earn-money-street-performers-busking-fund-dream-trips-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emusic%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20age%2013%2C%20he%20started%20attending%20community%20college%2C%20and%20at%2016%2C%20he%20was%20accepted%20to%20UCLA%20on%20a%20full%20scholarship%20to%20study%20music%20