cently%2C%20I%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20start%20adding%20a%20tariff%20tax%20line%20item%20directly%20to%20the%20price%20tags%20on%20certain%20products%20in%20our%20stores%2C%20especially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-bikes-popularity-sustainability-evs-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20bikes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20of%20our%20electric%20bikes%20from%20our%20major%20supplier%20are%20going%20to%20cost%2010%25%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20the%20exact%20same%20electric%20bikes%20hanging%20on%20the%20same%20hook%20in%20our%20retail%20stores%20and%20some%20cost%20%244%2C500%20and%20the%20one%20right%20next%20it%20costs%20%244%2C950.%20There's%20no%20difference%20except%20when%20we%20purchased%20them%2C%20so%20one%20has%20a%20line%20item%20because%20it%20was%20purchased%20when%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-raising-prices-increases-trump-tariffs-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprice%20increase%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20implemented%20due%20to%20the%20tariff.%20It%20really%20puts%20us%20in%20an%20uncomfortable%20situation%20with%20our%20customers.%20We%20have%20to%20explain%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20we%20like%20it%20or%20not%2C%20we're%20paying%20those%20taxes%2C%20which%20is%20how%20I%20view%20tariffs%2C%20as%20a%20brick-and-mortar%20shop.%20We%20have%20to%20pay%20it%20to%20get%20that%20product%20into%20our%20store.%20If%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20bike%20in%20a%20bike%20shop%2C%20I'm%20going%20out%20of%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20now%20the%20point%20comes%20to%2C%20are%20we%20going%20to%20pass%20that%20tax%20on%20to%20our%20customers%20or%20not%3F%20The%20bicycle%20industry%20runs%20on%20pretty%20tight%20margins.%20If%20you%20cut%20the%2010%25%20into%20that%2C%20you%20might%20as%20well%20get%20ready%20to%20have%20your%20exit%20strategy%20for%20your%20business%20because%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20operate.%20There's%20no%20way%2C%20that's%20just%20how%20it%20goes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ran%20for%20governor%20of%20Nevada%20in%202018%20as%20a%20Republican.%20I%20didn't%20vote%20for%20Donald%20Trump.%20He%20was%20the%20reason%20I%20ran%20for%20office.%20I%20watched%20how%20he%20was%20as%20a%20business%20person%2C%20and%20America's%20not%20a%20business.%20I%20feel%20like%20he%20doesn't%20understand%20how%20much%20of%20an%20impact%20his%20decisions%20have.%20He's%20almost%20got%20blinders%20on.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20that%20people%20need%20to%20be%20responsible%20for%20their%20actions.%20You%20can%20implement%20a%20policy%20that%20you%20think%20is%20great%20and%20we%20will%20back%20you%20up%2C%20but%20we're%20also%20going%20to%20tell%20everybody%20who's%20doing%20it.%20I%20have%20no%20problem%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanadian-stores-labeling-american-imports-consumers-responding-patriotism-trump-tariffs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elabeling%20where%20this%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20coming%20from%20on%20my%20products.%20People%20need%20to%20know%20that%20so%20I%20have%20a%20fighting%20chance%20on%20my%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariffs-effects-retailers-consumer-brands-hasbro-coca-cola-amazon-adidas-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariff%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20created%20chaos%20across%20the%20board.%20The%20uncertainty%20is%20absolutely%20insane.%20I%20ordered%20new%20sleeping%20bags%20from%20China%20for%20our%20summer%20tours%2C%20and%20I%20was%20just%20informed%20the%20supply%20chain%20has%20been%20disrupted%20and%20now%20I%20don't%20know%20when%20I%20will%20get%20that%20product%20or%20what%20I'm%20going%20to%20do.%20We're%20having%20to%20redo%20items%20that%20are%20time%20consuming%20during%20a%20season%20where%20we%20should%20be%20focusing%20on%20our%20customer's%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20business%20owner%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20time%20for%20this%20baloney.%20I%20did%20my%20planning%20already%20in%20my%20slow%20season.%20It's%20really%20disruptive%20in%20my%20operations%20for%20me%20to%20have%20to%20go%20and%20find%20items%20for%20something%20that%20I've%20already%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20also%20seeing%20the%20effects%20on%20our%20tourism%20business.%20We%20have%20lots%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanadians-canceling-us-travel-earnings-visiting-mexico-europe-carribean-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECanadian%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20when%20all%20this%20tariff%20talk%20started%2C%20they%20began%20canceling%20tours.%20These%20are%20%242%2C000%20to%20%244%2C000%20cancellations.%20One%20group%20told%20us%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20love%20you%20guys%2C%20but%20we%20can't%20put%20our%20money%20into%20America%20because%20of%20what%20they're%20doing%20and%20what%20they're%20saying%20about%20our%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tariffs%20affect%20everything%20at%20some%20level%3A%20some%20very%20big%20and%20some%20you%20won't%20even%20notice.%20It's%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20little%20cuts%20and%20eventually%20you%20bleed%20out.%20Enough's%20enough%20and%20people%20will%20shut%20their%20doors.%20The%20one%20word%20I%20could%20say%20for%20this%20whole%20problem%20that%20we're%20facing%20is%20unnecessary.%20It%20doesn't%20need%20to%20happen%2C%20but%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20tariffs%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Akvlamis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ekvlamis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frepublican-business-owner-tariff-tax-line-item-price-tags-transparency-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A