igrant%2C%20I%20faced%20complexities%20in%20immigration%20and%20cultural%20adaptation%2C%20and%20I%20also%20had%20to%20build%20a%20professional%20network%20from%20scratch.%20I%20found%20four%20techniques%20that%20helped%20me%20design%20my%20career%20path%20to%20gain%20internships%20and%20then%20my%20full-time%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217762f92-c19a-47b6-9ed4-6de07717e320%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Be%20proactive%20and%20start%20building%20your%20career%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20volunteered%20at%20my%20university%20to%20set%20up%20a%20booth%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-grace-hopper-celebration-women-in-tech-google-snap-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrace%20Hopper%20Celebration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20major%20convention%20for%20women%20in%20computing%20where%20people%20come%20to%20find%20internship%20opportunities%20and%20network.%20I%20received%20a%20partial%20scholarship%20to%20attend%20the%20career%20fair%2C%20and%20my%20university%20paid%20for%20the%20trip%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20secured%20my%20summer%20internship%20at%20McAfee%20by%20talking%20to%20a%20recruiter%20there%20who%20was%20also%20a%20graduate%20of%20UT%20Arlington.%20We%20connected%2C%20and%20I%20shared%20my%20journey%20with%20her.%20She%20loved%20my%20story%20and%20gave%20me%20an%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20to%20start%20early%20during%20your%20first%20year%20of%20college%20or%20grad%20school.%20Talk%20to%20your%20university's%20career%20counselors%20and%20ask%20them%20what%20kind%20of%20scholarships%20and%20career%20fairs%20the%20universities%20represent.%20Can%20I%20volunteer%20there%3F%20Can%20you%20give%20me%20a%20scholarship%20to%20attend%20a%20certain%20program%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20way%20you%20can%20kick-start%20your%20career%20and%20seize%20an%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22426eb289-e781-4b70-8503-0e3597819e88%5C%22%3E%3Cstron