6quot%3BShe%20could%20be%20very%20happy%20with%20two%20or%20three%20or%20four%20or%20five%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBob%20Ferrari%2C%20a%20supply%20chain%20executive%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20Ferrari%20Consulting%20and%20Research%20Group%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-increase-prices-empty-shelves-timeline-supply-chain-holidays-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow-margin%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20including%20toys%20%E2%80%94%20that%20companies%20don't%20make%20a%20huge%20profit%20from%20could%20see%20price%20increases%20and%20low%20inventory%20before%20other%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223a8d9755-7794-46cc-8abe-a20017b04fe7%5C%22%3EThe%20political%20fallout%20for%20Trump%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20reason%20US%20politicians%20generally%20don't%20talk%20about%20Americans%2C%20especially%20children%2C%20making%20do%20with%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20President%20Franklin%20D.%20Roosevelt%20calling%20on%20the%20American%20public%20to%20make%20sacrifices%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20Trump's%20call%20for%20girls%20to%20sacrifice%20their%20dolls%20is%20%26quot%3Bstrikingly%20ill-informed%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20Frank%2C%20a%20professor%20emeritus%20of%20rhetoric%20and%20political%20communication%20at%20University%20of%20Oregon%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrank%20noted%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbudgetlab.yale.edu%2Fresearch%2Fwhere-we-stand-fiscal-economic-and-distributional-effects-all-us-tariffs-enacted-2025-through-april%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Budget%20Lab%20at%20Yale%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%20estimates%20that%20Trump's%20tariffs%20will%20reduce%20the%20after-tax%20income%20of%20low-income%20households%20by%204%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20not%20households%20with%2037%20dolls%20and%20250%20pencils%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20sort%20of%20rhetoric%20of%20making%20do%20with%20less%20could%20hurt%20the%20president's%20standing%20with%20some%20of%20his%20supporters%2C%20Ethan%20Porter%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20media%20and%20public%20affairs%20at%20George%20Washington%20University%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20is%20trying%20to%20persuade%20people%20to%20accept%20less%2C%20but%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20people%20are%20going%20to%20feel%20deprived%2C%20and%20Americans%20don't%20like%20to%20feel%20deprived%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20sabotaged%20his%20own%20greatest%20strength%2C%20which%20is%20his%20understanding%20of%20the%20American%20consumer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219b50622-b2bb-4405-b7e4-0697663977c6%5C%22%3EEmpty%20shelves%20and%20a%20bleak%20Christmas%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnless%20Trump%20reverses%20the%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20goods%20%E2%80%94%20and%20soon%20%E2%80%94%20the%20levies%20will%20have%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20American%20consumers%2C%20who%20will%20start%20to%20see%20higher%20prices%20and%20a%20smaller%20inventory%20of%20toys%2C%20both%20online%20and%20on%20the%20shelves%2C%20Velte%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump-themed%20stuffed%20toy%20ducks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6806597bc6ad288d147ead63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrump-themed%20stuffed%20toy%20ducks%20could%20be%20seen%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20last%20year.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FSusan%20Walsh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere'll%20be%20a%20shortage%20of%20product%2C%20number%20one%2C%20because%20some%20products%20just%20won't%20come%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere'll%20be%20some%20products%20that%20do%20come%20in%20but%20will%20be%20delayed%2C%20and%20then%20some%20products%20you%20just%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20afford.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20the%20companies%20that%20stocked%20extra%20inventory%20ahead%20of%20the%20tariffs%2C%20those%20products%20will%20sell%20out%20quickly%2C%20resulting%20in%20longer%20lines%20and%20emptier%20shelves%2C%20Velte%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20very%20sad%20Christmas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELynn%20Rosenblum%2C%20a%20consumer%20products%20expert%2C%20echoed%20Velte's%20concern%20about%20empty%20toy%20shelves%20ahead%20of%20the%20holiday%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3EUsually%20in%20the%20toy%20industry%2C%20an%20empty%20shelf%20means%20that%20you've%20sold%20out%2C%20and%20that's%20actually%20a%20good%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenblum%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20just%20think%20that%20there%20might%20be%20less%20choices%2C%20at%20least%20for%20the%20short%20term%20and%20maybe%20the%20long%20term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20toy%20behemoth%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fs201.q4cdn.com%2F696436908%2Ffiles%2Fdoc_financials%2F2025%2Fq1%2FMattel-Q1-2025-Financial-Results-Presentation.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMattel%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20it%20might%20have%20to%20raise%20its%20prices%20in%20the%20US%20to%20offset%20the%20impact%20of%20Trump's%20tariff%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20volatile%20macroeconomic%20environment%20and%20evolving%20US%20tariff%20situation%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20predict%20consumer%20spending%20and%20Mattel's%20US%20sales%20in%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20year%20and%20holiday%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company's%20most%20recent%20earnings%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOcean%20freight%20bookings%20of%20containers%20shipping%20from%20China%20to%20the%20US%20are%20down%20significantly%2C%20nosediving%2042.7%25%20for%20the%20week%20of%20April%2028%20%E2%80%94%20the%20sharpest%20weekly%20drop%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20digital%20logistics%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vizionapi.com%2Fblog%2Ftariff-tracker%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVizion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dc5daef9-0bd2-4ad2-9752-bbb9d28182e0%5C%22%3ERebuilding%20toy%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20US%20could%20take%20years%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20massive%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20industries%20like%20toy%20manufacturing%20will%20be%20able%20to%20quickly%20scale%20up%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20mold-making%20for%20plastic%20products%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20something%20that%20is%20highly%20specialized%2C%26quot%3B%20Jason%20Miller%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20supply%20chain%20management%20at%20Michigan%20State%20University%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThe%20ecosystem%20for%20toy%20production%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20for%20the%20US%2C%20but%20really%20for%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20is%20in%20China.%20That%20ecosystem%20isn't%20something%20that%20can%20up%20and%20move%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20Steinberg%2C%20a%20toy%20expert%20and%20the%20creator%20of%20The%20Modern%20Parent's%20Guide%20book%20series%2C%20echoed%20those%20concerns.%20%26quot%3BTo%20get%20the%20kind%20of%20manufacturing%20capabilities%20to%20make%20toys%20in%20the%20US%20that%20the%20administration%20is%20hoping%20for%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20more%20like%20a%20five-to-seven%20year%20process%20of%20investments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Mattel%20CEO%20Ynon%20Kreiz%20said%20manufacturing%20for%20the%20company%20wasn't%20returning%20stateside%20anytime%20soon.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20see%20that%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20Kreiz%20said%20on%20CNBC's%20Squawk%20Box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consequences%20of%20tariffs%20for%20the%20industry%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Bdevastating%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenblum%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20thinks%20of%20the%20big%20toy%20companies%20when%20they%20think%20of%20the%20industry%2C%20but%20a%20very%20large%20percentage%20of%20the%20industry%20are%20entrepreneurs%2C%20small%20toy%20companies%2C%20midsize%20toy%20companies%2C%20and%20just%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20businesses%2C%20folks%20that%20can't%20keep%20their%20doors%20open%2C%20can't%20keep%20their%20employees%20paid%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-toy-industry-impact-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746608461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681a146a3fe8d39283650a89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-toy-industry-impact-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Experts%20say%20that%20Trump's%20tariffs%20could%20cause%20a%20shortage%20of%20toys%2C%20price%20hikes%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20sad%20Christmas.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20L.%20Dorman%2CGrace%20Eliza%20Goodwin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-toy-industry-impact-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sehwag%20reacts%20on%20'Operation%20Sindoor'%3A%20'Agar%20koi%20aap%20par%20patthar%20...%20'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746608441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120959755%2Cimgsize-20766.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fvirender-sehwag-reacts-on-operation-sindoor-agar-koi-aap-par-patthar-phenke-%2Farticleshow%2F120959658.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Following%20the%20Pahalgam%20terror%20attack%2C%20India%20launched%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Sindoor%26quot%3B%20on%20May%207%2C%20targeting%20terror%20launchpads%20across%20Pakistan%20and%20Pakistan-Occupied%20Kashmir.%20Virender%20Sehwag%20an