m%3E(spiced%20chickpeas%20served%20with%20soft%20leavened%20flatbread)%20he%20grew%20up%20eating%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Sagar%20took%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%2C%20leaving%20behind%20a%20secure%20career%20to%20pursue%20a%20project%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20entirely%20sure%20about.%20Motivated%20by%20his%20love%20for%20food%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20turn%20his%20passion%20into%20a%20business.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20all%20started%20with%20my%20desire%20to%20bring%20the%20authentic%20taste%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20That%20one%20thought%20eventually%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first-ever%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20vending%20machine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BHome%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A0%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faarohan.infosys.org%2F%3Fcmpid%3Dsco_TheBetterIndia_EB_AarohanAwards25_foundation_banner_24042025_lq_Awareness_Rgn%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Vice%20President%20to%20building%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20vending%20machine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Janakpuri%2C%20West%20Delhi%2C%20Sagar%20always%20had%20an%20unshakable%20love%20for%20food%2C%20especially%20the%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20his%20hometown.%20%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%20in%20Delhi%2C%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20a%20staple.%20But%20when%20I%20lived%20in%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20Mumbai%2C%20I%20could%20never%20find%20the%20same%20authentic%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remembers.%20The%20craving%20for%20that%20delicious%20and%20spicy%20%3Cem%3Echhole%3C%2Fem%3E%20never%20left%20him.%20He%20would%20often%20wonder%20why%20North%20India%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20food%20is%20not%20available%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20over%2014%20years%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20prestigious%20banks%20like%20Citibank%20and%20Credit%20Suisse%2C%20steadily%20climbing%20the%20corporate%20ladder.%20Even%20though%20he%20was%20fond%20of%20his%20full-time%20job%2C%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20shake%20off%20the%20idea%20of%20doing%20something%20of%20his%20own.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20during%20a%20senior%20management%20programme%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%20in%202023%20that%20I%20met%20people%20who%20were%20doing%20things%20beyond%20their%20regular%20jobs%2C%20including%20CEOs%2C%20entrepreneurs%2C%20and%20bloggers.%20That%20made%20me%20realise%20that%20if%20they%20can%20do%20it%2C%20so%20can%20I%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-02T175712.650_11zon-1746188865.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sagar%20spent%20countless%20hours%20on%20research%20and%20reading%20to%20build%20the%20perfect%20chhole%20kulche%20vending%20machine%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-02T175712.650_11zon-1746188865.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-02T175712.650_11zon-1746188865-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-02T175712.650_11zon-1746188865-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-02T175712.650_11zon-1746188865-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-02T175712.650_11zon-1746188865-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-424649%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESagar%20spent%20countless%20hours%20on%20research%20and%20reading%20to%20build%20the%20perfect%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%20%3C%2Fem%3Evending%20machine%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20much%20thought%20and%20countless%20conversations%2C%20Sagar%20decided%20to%20create%20a%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20vending%20machine%20that%20would%20make%20the%20customers%20feel%20like%20they%20were%20eating%20from%20a%20roadside%20vendor%20in%20Delhi%2C%20without%20compromising%20on%20the%20consistency%2C%20freshness%2C%20and%20authenticity.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F211235%2Findia-hot-vending-machines-home-food-chef-women-delhi-startup-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethought%20of%20vending%20machines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20knew%20they%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20solve%20three%20big%20problems%3A%20hygiene%2C%20time%2C%20and%20consistency%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20entrepreneur%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D